---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Musanze - Gateway to Rwanda's Mountain Gorillas">
  <Header />
  
  <div style="padding-top: 120px;" class="s">
    <div class="s-narrow" style="margin: 0 auto;">
      <span class="s-label">Gorilla Trekking</span>
      <h1 class="s-heading">Musanze<br><em>Land of Mist & Gorillas</em></h1>
      <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
        <img src="/images/rwanda_gorilla_nature_1763982585054.png" alt="Mountain gorilla in Volcanoes National Park" style="width:100%; border-radius: 8px;">
      </div>
      <div class="s-body" style="max-width: 100%;">
        <p>Musanze, formerly known as Ruhengeri, is the gateway to Volcanoes National Park — home to the world's remaining mountain gorillas. Nestled in the shadow of five ancient volcanoes, this highland town offers one of Africa's most extraordinary wildlife encounters.</p>
        
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--gold);">Top Attractions</h3>
        <ul style="margin-top: 1rem; list-style-position: inside;">
          <li>🦍 Gorilla Trekking — once-in-a-lifetime encounter with mountain gorillas</li>
          <li>🌋 Mount Bisoke Hike — crater lake at the volcano summit</li>
          <li>🦧 Golden Monkey Trekking — playful primates in bamboo forests</li>
          <li>🕯️ Musanze Caves — ancient lava tubes stretching 2km underground</li>
          <li>🏞️ Iby'iwacu Cultural Village — traditional Rwandan village experience</li>
          <li>📸 Dian Fossey Grave — tribute to the legendary primatologist</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--gold);">Gorilla Trekking Tips</h3>
        <p>Permits cost $1,500 per person and must be booked months in advance. The trek can take 2-6 hours depending on where the gorilla family has moved. Wear sturdy hiking boots, bring rain gear, and hire a porter to support the local community.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box" style="background: var(--bg2); padding: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);">
          <h4 style="color: var(--gold);">Permit Information</h4>
          <p>Gorilla permits are limited to 96 per day. Book 3-6 months in advance through the Rwanda Development Board or let us secure your permit as part of a complete trekking package.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>